    "video_length": "PT7M25S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "Before getting to the heart of the matter,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "let me begin by [br]asking you, the audience,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a quick question.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would like to know[br]how many of you", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "consume bottled mineral water[br]on a regular basis?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Can you turn on the light [br]in the room please?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Raise your hand, all those [br]who consume bottled mineral water.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Perfect.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I see that it holds for [br]about 90% of you.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I did a little exercise,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I collected the equivalent [br]of one person&#39;s consumption", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of plastic bottles in a year.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Considering that a person consumes [br]about 1 litre of water a day.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And in fact, quite simply, [br]it looks like this.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s it...[br]Sorry, I forgot the essential.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There, all you see here...", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, it&#39;s 12 kilos.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It is 12 kilos of plastic [br]for just one person!", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then let&#39;s do a little maths to see", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "our collective impact today:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we are about 400 in this room,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so I&#39;ve been told.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Suppose there were 390 of you [br]who raised your hand", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when I asked my question.[br]I&#39;ll multiply 390 x 12", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to know what our impact is[br]this year, in 2013.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, imagine that, [br]all together in this room,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we will have thrown away [br]4.7 tons of plastic this year,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "after just a few sips of water,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and this plastic will take between [br]200 to 400 years to break down in nature.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, you&#39;ll tell me,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "logically, we could recycle all that.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, when we know [br]the collection sorting recycle circuit", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the recycling of waste [br]in Morocco looks like this,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that is quite simply informal collectors", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "working in the worst conditions that are,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- some even work with [br]their nose in our waste all day,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that&#39;s just at [br]the Mediouna waste dump", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in Casablanca --", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "well, I can assure you that [br]90% of our waste will end up", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as a source of direct pollution in nature,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as we can see in this photo,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that, unfortunately,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has been taken [br]in a Moroccan countryside.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Seeing that, I wanted to act.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I wanted to start with myself.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As a citizen, I want to explore", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "all the opportunities[br]that are in my power", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to reduce my waste output,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and, therefore, reduce[br]my contribution to this problem.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I challenged myself to what I called", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the Zero Zbel Xperience.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Quite simply, I set myself the goal,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "until December 31st this year,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to reach zero waste in my daily life.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How did I start?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I started by weighing my waste,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because you need to know [br]where you start", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "... to find out where you&#39;re going.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In one month, during which[br]I weighed my waste,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I produced 15 kilos of waste,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just by myself:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s still only half the average [br]output of a French person;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "4 times less than the average [br]waste of an American,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but it&#39;s still 180 kilos of waste", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I have produced, [br]just by myself, in a year;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I find it quite simply aberrant.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think it&#39;s huge.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My first instinct to act on it,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I thought to myself,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I will find ways to recycle it myself.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I grabbed a pair of scissors,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a bit of creativity,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I said to myself,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m going to cut up all that, [br]I&#39;ll make flower pots,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ll make pen-holders,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ll make lampshades,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but very quickly, I realized", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I was going to spend all my time", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that my house [br]would become a sort of museum", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of totally useless recycled objects.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I quickly came to [br]the very simple conclusion,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that the best way [br]to reduce my waste", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is simply to avoid producing[br]as much waste as possible.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s called reduction at source.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What is reduction at source?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It is very simple, [br]because the source is me,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the source is you,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s us when we buy and consume.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, for this reduction at the root, [br]I adopted two principles.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The first is", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to avoid anything that comes [br]prepackaged in plastic bags,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and always prefer natural products.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The second is,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "avoid waste, and especially food waste,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that is, I&#39;ll buy and cook", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "only what I can consume,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to avoid food getting spoiled,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in my closet and my fridge, [br]which I don&#39;t eat.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This being said,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ll give you a small example[br]to illustrate", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how I reduce my waste.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ll take a very simple example.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The wicker basket,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which is an object of our daily lives", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or at least it was an everyday object", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for our parents and our grandparents.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Before I wrapped my head around [br]reducing my waste,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "going shopping, for example,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to buy vegetables, [br]I would end up with this!", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Plastic.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would end up with [br]1 kilo of carrots in a plastic bag,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "1 kilo of cucumbers in a plastic bag", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and 1 kilo of tomatoes in a plastic bag.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s 3 kilos, of course,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "each in a plastic bag", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and to transport them back home,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they were not in -one- plastic bag,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but -two- plastic bags,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to make sure that [br]between the market and home,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the bag does not break", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I end up with[br]my vegetables on the ground.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So it&#39;s simply 5 plastic bags,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "used in a totally useless way,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when we know that I could have had [br]the same products", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in my wicker basket [br]with no waste to go with it.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What I&#39;m telling you", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is that I&#39;ve eliminated, in fact I&#39;ve replaced [br]hundreds of plastic bags", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I use in a year by a wicker basket,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I eliminated [br]and reduced hundreds of bottles", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I would have consumed in one year", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by a glass bottle,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I fill and refill whenever I&#39;m thirsty,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and if you don&#39;t like tap water,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you can still filter it.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All that being said,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I invite you to dream with me:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "imagine that I&#39;ve been[br]sufficiently compelling today,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so that you, [br]and 30 million Moroccans compatriots,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "decide, starting today, [br]to slightly reduce your waste.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m not telling you[br]to get to zero as I am doing,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but reduce a little.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, it would make so much less waste", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for the State to manage,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so much less money to spend", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for the collection [br]and the management of our waste.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So logically, that much money [br]made available for the State budget", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to be invested in other areas,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "such as health or education,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which are priority areas;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It would also make so much less [br]agricultural land mobilized", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to create waste dumps;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that would represent, if you [br]think about it, so much less", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to invest when the State wants", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to develop a sector of sorting, collecting [br]and recycling our waste", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that is modern and efficient.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you see,[br]starting with small everyday gestures", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like those I showed you,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we end up with positive effects [br]which add up and multiply.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My message today is very simple.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When faced with a big problem [br]such as Morocco&#39;s waste,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the simplest solutions", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are just those at our level,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "us, the citizens.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we just have to get down to it, [br]each of us,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a tiny bit on a daily basis.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I can assure you that all together", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we can succeed in having[br]a very big impact,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we can solve a problem", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "such as that of waste in Morocco.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thank you.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }
    ], 
